		- kldp.org

		- [\w-]+.kldp.org:

			- banner
			- bbs
			- blog
			- cert
			- css-validator
			- feedvalidator
			- gallery
			- geekforum
			- img
			- open
			- people
			- weblog
			- wiki
			- www


	Mixed content:

		- Images, on:

			- banner from validator ¹
			- banner from css-validator ¹
			- banner from img ¹
			- css-validator from www.w3.org ²
			- validator from $self ¹
			- validator from validator.w3.org ²

		- Ad on banner from oops.org ¹

	¹ Secured by us
	² Unsecurable			- 

